Usage: boat auth

Interactively setup local Longboat token for API access and CLI tools.

First create a token via the Longboat website: https://gorm.longboat.io
Then run 'boat auth' to enable API access and the Longboat CLI Tools.

If you don't have a Longboat user yet, you can either run 'boat register'
or you can signup via the website: https://gorm.longboat.io

